</pre></div></div>
<p class="noindent">ç¶šã„ã¦ã€ãƒ†ã‚¹ãƒˆã‚¹ã‚¤ãƒ¼ãƒˆã‚’å®Ÿè¡Œã—ã¦ <span style="color: ForestGreen"><span class="sc"></span><span class="sc"><strong>green</strong></span><span class="sc"></span></span>ã«ãªã‚‹ã‹ç¢ºèªã—ã€å•é¡Œãªã‘ã‚Œã°Bitbucketã«ãƒ—ãƒƒã‚·ãƒ¥ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>
<div class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre><span class="gp">$</span> rails <span class="nb">test</span>
<span class="gp">$</span><span class="nb"> </span>git push
</pre></div></div>
<p class="noindent">æœ€å¾Œã«ã€Herokuã¸ãƒ‡ãƒ—ãƒ­ã‚¤ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>
